overview: Goldberg battles Scott Hall in a Stun Gun Ladder Match. "The Nature Boy" Ric Flair joins forces with son David Flair to face Barry Windham & Curt Hennig. Chris Jericho clashes with Perry Saturn. Billy Kidman, Rey Misterio Jr., Juventud Guerrera, and Psicosis compete for the WCW Cruiserweight Championship and so much more!
title: WCW Souled Out 1999
